channel.title: 508 ip changer gets stuck
channel.description: When I load my ip changer and put in a server's ip that i've played before, it loads and gets stuck on "Connecting to update server." I've checked the status of the servers and they're up but the ip changers I use get stuck on it. Then it says "error_game_js5connect." Can anybody help me?
